title: Cole's Logo Emporium
content:
[[include :scp-wiki:theme:word-processor]]

[[module css]]
#header h1 a::before {
    content: "Cole's Logo Emporium";
    color: #333;
    font-family: 'Baloo Bhaina 2', cursive;
}
 #header h2 span {
   color: transparent;
   text-shadow: none;
}
#header h2 span::before {
    content: '"Insert Logo Here"';
    color: #0F4699;
    font-family: 'Baloo Bhaina 2', cursive;
}
[[/module]]
[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]
[[=]]
Hello! I'm [[*user Cole 13]]. I've been playing around with making logos so here they are! If you want, feel free to use the logos! Just PM me so I know where to look!
[[/=]]
